Battera:
She jumped down from the table and smiled. Her wings and body looked 
rougher around the edges. Her claws were longer and much sharper. Her 
optics were red and not blue. Her voice was a little rougher and her 
words sounded harsher. She smiled and looked at Kup. "You know, when 
this is all done, and if I make it, could you pleae reverse all this. 
I feel like the worst slag heap this side of Cyberton."

She walked out and looked down the hall. "Well, the only thing I need 
is the insignia of the proud predacons and I'm set to find this bot 
of yours. What is her name and what did she look like?"
